The%20bathroom.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20motion-sensor%20under-counter%20light%20that%20helps%20employees%20find%20their%20way%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20hairdryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERagan%20said%20the%20shower%20is%20particuarly%20unique%20as%20the%20shower%20head%20and%20the%20nob%20to%20turn%20it%20on%20and%20control%20the%20temperature%20are%20on%20opposite%20sides.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223087%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20shower%20and%20toiletries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66477dcc9fc063e829b25f85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222315%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20shower%20head%20is%20on%20the%20other%20side.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20explained%20that%20bulk%20toiletries%20are%20part%20of%20the%20complex's%20effort%20to%20reduce%20waste%2C%20particularly%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shower%20door%20closes%20all%20the%20way%20to%20ensure%20no%20mess%20or%20splashing%20like%20in%20some%20hotels.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAviation-themed%20art%20nod%20to%20the%20airline%20without%20being%20overbearing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Artwork%20on%20the%20walls%20showing%20a%20paper%20airplane%20and%20one%20with%20clouds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66477e9614fb5b23cc5dd153%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222858%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20artwork%20varies%20room%20to%20room%2C%20Ragan%20said.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20will%20change%20from%20room%20to%20room%2C%20but%20the%20overall%20layout%20and%20size%20of%20each%20space%20are%20exactly%20the%20same.%20Ragan%20said%20this%20ensures%20there%20isn't%20a%20hierarchy%20among%20team%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAside%20from%20the%20expected%20hotel%20amenities%2C%20American%20has%20added%20a%20few%20special%20touches%20based%20on%20employee%20feedback.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ottoman%20has%20a%20seatbelt%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66477f2e9fc063e829b26366%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican's%20private%20hotel%20operates%20like%20any%20other%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20housekeeping%20service.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERagan%20said%20the%20input%20of%20American%20flight%20crewmembers%2C%20who%20stay%20in%20hotel%20rooms%20far%20more%20than%20the%20average%20person%2C%20was%20essential%20in%20creating%20the%20hotel%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20example%2C%20Ragan%20said%20crews%20travel%20with%20clips%20to%20hold%20curtains%20together%20and%20keep%20light%20out%2C%20so%20a%20magnet%20was%20added%20to%20make%20them%20easier%20to%20latch.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20clamping%20the%20curtains%20shut.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66477f8720abc1efe8fb1faf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221978%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20clamping%20the%20curtains%20shut.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20curtains%20also%20have%20a%20slight%20drag%20to%20ensure%20the%20slit%20at%20the%20bottom%20doesn't%20let%20in%20any%20light%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20crew-specific%20amenity%20is%20a%20board%20to%20pin%20up%20their%20'paper%20tiger%2C'%20which%20is%20a%20poster%20diagram%20of%20the%20cockpit%20required%20for%20pilot%20training.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20board%20where%20pilots%20can%20hang%20up%20their%20cockpit%20diagrams.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664780a89fc063e829b26524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20board%20where%20pilots%20can%20hang%20up%20their%20cockpit%20diagrams%2C%20which%20are%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3Bpaper%20tigers.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20little%20details%20that%20resulted%20from%20feedback%20from%20our%20team%20members%20will%20make%20the%20employee%20visits%20more%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Ragan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeanwhile%2C%20employees%20asked%20that%20there%20be%20no%20microwaves%20in%20the%20rooms%20to%20avoid%20unwanted%20smells%20like%20burned%20popcorn.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Keurig%2C%20coffee%20pods%2C%20and%20refrigerator%20in%20the%20hotel%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647814220abc1efe8fb22e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rooms%20have%20a%20safe%20(top%20drawer%20in%20the%20pictured%20dresser)%20that%20is%20big%20enough%20to%20hold%20a%20standard-sized%20laptop.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERagan%20said%20there%20is%20microwave%20capability%20on%20the%20main%20floor%20for%20employees%20who%20need%20it%20and%20that%20other%20kitchen%20equipment%20like%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20Keurig%20are%20available%20in%20the%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20closet%20area%20features%20plenty%20of%20hanging%20space%20for%20uniforms%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20full-body%20mirror.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20closet%20with%20beige%20hangars.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664781b99fc063e829b2663e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3C