%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sitting%20area%20outside%20the%20food%20hall%20stretches%20into%20a%20large%20courtyard%20where%20employees%20can%20access%20sports%20courts%20and%20walking%20trails.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223855%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20courtyard%20outside%20Skyview%206.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647851920abc1efe8fb2650%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222891%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20courtyard%20outside%20Skyview%206%20hosts%20some%20400%20new%20trees%20and%20rocks%20that%20were%20excavated%20from%20the%20original%20Stewardess%20College.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20have%20access%20to%20a%20basketball%20court%2C%20tennis%20court%2C%20pickleball%20court%2C%20and%20beach%20volleyball%20court.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sign%20inside%20the%20fitness%20center%20posted%20a%20volleyball%20tournament%20being%20held%20later%20that%20week%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20to%20sign%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20cool%20to%20see%20those%20community%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20courtyard%20is%20the%20'Globe%20of%20Firsts.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20%26quot%3BGlobe%20of%20Firsts%26quot%3B%20sitting%20in%20the%20courtyard%20surrounded%20by%20trees%20with%20the%20hotel%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647859d14fb5b23cc5dda7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGlobe%20of%20Firsts.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2012-foot%20stainless%20steel%20sculpture%20features%20names%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-woman-pilot-major-us-airline-american-1973-uniform-girl-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBonnie%20Tiburzi%2C%20the%20first