0because%20the%20company%20is%20100%25%20remote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20point%20of%20it%20was%20to%20be%20silly%20and%20to%20put%20people%20in%20different%20environments%20and%20situations%20where%20they%20could%20create%20new%20networks%20and%20pathways%20to%20people%20in%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuildkite's%20zeal%20for%20zaniness%20%E2%80%94%20one%20employee%20holds%20the%20unofficial%20title%20of%20Dome%2C%20the%20director%20of%20musical%20entertainment%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0aims%20to%20drive%20workers'%20collaboration%20and%20innovation.%20Those%20are%20the%20stated%20aims%20of%20many%20CEOs%20when%20they%20call%20workers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-calling-workers-back-to-the-office-focused-wrong-thing-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20into%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20at%20least%20part%20of%20the%20workweek.%20But%20Pitt%20sees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-level-job-seekers-quit-over-return-to-office-requirement-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid's%20halfsies%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20misguided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20worst%20of%20both%20worlds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keith%20Pitt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664505f87415a05fdd08a08e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKeith%20Pitt%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Buildkite.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Buildkite%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPitt%20calls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-here-to-stay-ceos-rto-remote-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20setups%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%26quot%3Bscheduling%20and%20policy%20nightmare.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20sitting%20in%20a%20meeting%20where%20some%20people%20are%20gathered%20in%20a%20room%20and%20one%20or%20more%20are%20dialed%20in%20from%20elsewhere%20can%20lead%20to%20people%20not%20hearing%20each%20other%20and%20virtual%20attendees%20missing%20out%20on%20what%20goes%20on%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20hybrid%20environment%2C%20remote%20is%20always%20second%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c7cea03-c84a-492a-9db1-aaff52f0068f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20connections%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPitt%2C%2036%2C%20isn't%20anti-office.%20At%20age%2017%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20of%20high%20school%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20programmer.%20He%20did%20the%20commute%20and%20wore%20a%20suit%20to%20work%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20in%202013%2C%20when%20Pitt%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Perth%2C%20Australia%2C%20started%20Buildkite%2C%20it%20never%20occurred%20to%20him%20to%20set%20up%20an%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20makes%20a%20DevOps%20platform%20used%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20Airbnb%2C%20Doordash%2C%20and%20Slack%2C%20among%20others.%20Starting%20out%2C%20money%20needed%20to%20go%20to%20web%20servers%2C%20not%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitt%20said%20the%20135-person%20company%20funnels%20part%20of%20what%20it%20isn't%20spending%20on%20facilities%20into%20%26quot%3Bconnection%20budgets.%26quot%3B%20They%20fund%20the%20annual%20all-employee%20gathering%20and%20smaller%20trips%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20let%20coworkers%20get%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20rent%20a%20coworking%20space%2C%20and%20collab%20IRL%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20last%20in-person%20all-hands%20came%20to%20about%20300%2C000%20Australian%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20cheap%20as%20chips%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBest%20money%20ever%20spent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuildkite%20also%20spends%20on%20remote%20activities%20meant%20to%20foster%20connection.%20There%20are%20virtual%20gatherings%20for%20doing%20puzzles%20or%20quizzes%20about%20music%20or%20movies.%20The%20company%20has%20held%20cooking%20events%20where%20it%20pays%20workers%20to%20buy%20ingredients%2C%20and%20colleagues%20make%20a%20meal%20together%20over%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20all%20the%20fun%20meant%20to%20boost%20camaraderie%2C%20Buildkite's%20culture%20is%20serious%20about%20working%20from%20home%2C%20Pitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20are%20given%20a%20budget%20of%203%2C000%20Australian%20dollars%20to%20trick%20out%20their%20home%20offices.%20The%20company%20asks%20new%20hires%20to%20take%20pictures%20of%20their%20setups%20to%20ensure%20they%20have%20a%20quiet%20space%20with%20a%20proper%20desk%20and%20chair%20to%20avoid%20ergonomic%20fails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20foster%20a%20work-from-the-couch%2C%20work-from-the-kitchen-table%20type%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20encourage%20people%20to%20throw%20some%20paint%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20buy%20some%20plants%2C%20buy%20some%20new%20artwork%2C%20just%20to%20change%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20also%20need%20high-quality%20equipment%3A%20A%20poor%20camera%20or%20mic%2C%20Pitt%20said%2C%20is%20the%20digital%20equivalent%20of%20having%20something%20stuck%20in%20your%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eea3b67e-ddb8-41d5-9e6d-8d9cffaecc24%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20easy%20to%20look%20busy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20the%20company%20tackles%20remote%20work%20for%20an%20employee%20base%20spread%20around%20the%20world%20is%20to%20cluster%20some%20functions.%20Buildkite%20uses%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Btimezone%20bubbles.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20for%20product%20and%20engineering%2C%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20plus%20or%20minus%20four%20hours%20from%20Sydney's%20time%20zone.%20For%20sales%20and%20marketing%2C%20it's%20the%20western%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20helps%20to%20ensure%20coworkers%20are%20generally%20online%20simultaneously%20and%20not%20left%20waiting%20for%20responses%20from%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20work%20Buildkite%20has%20done%20to%20establish%20norms%20around%20having%20what%20Pitt%20refers%20to%20as%20135%20small%20offices%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0one%20for%20each%20employee%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0he%20sees%20Buildkite's%20embrace%20of%20remote%20work%20as%20a%20long-term%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20eager%20to%20see%20how%20this%20thing%20plays%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20For%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20working.%20The%20company%20is%20on%20track%20to%20hire%2050%20people%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20dwelling%20on%20where%20workers%20work%2C%20a%20big%20focus%20is%20on%20developing%20trust%2C%20Pitt%20said.%20He%20thinks%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20some%20bosses%20are%20demanding%20workers%20be%20back%20in%20the%20office%20is%20because%20they%20don't%20trust%20their%20teams.%20But%2C%20Pitt%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20easy%20to%20look%20busy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitt%20said%20building%20trust%20can%20be%20harder%20when%20people%20aren't%20face-to-face.%20Playing%20games%20with%20colleagues%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bshortcut%26quot%3B%20he's%20found%20to%20developing%20that%20faith%20in%20colleagues%20beyond%20completing%20projects%20together%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20part%20of%20why%20he%20occasionally%20gets%20workers%20together.%20After%20the%20last%20all-worker%20event%2C%20the%20number%20of%20employees%20who%20reported%20feeling%20more%20connected%20to%20their%20teams%20and%20the%20company%20more%20than%20quadrupled.%20Now%2C%20Buildkite%20runs%20employee%20sentiment%20surveys%20every%20couple%20of%20months.%20And%20when%20it%20dips%20below%20a%20certain%20level%2C%20the%20company%20will%20announce%20another%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20keep%20trust%20elevated%20because%20that's%20when%20workers%20do%20their%20best%2C%20Pitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrust%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20being%20able%20to%20come%20up%20with%20creative%20ideas%20on%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20Pitt%20said%2C%20if%20workers%20care%20about%20the%20mission%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20they%20work%20in%20an%20office%20or%20from%20afar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20want%20to%20do%20the%20work%20because%20it's%20fun%20and%20it's%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%20with%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-worst-of-both-worlds-remote-ceo-says-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716025322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664509c59fc063e829b1670d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-worst-of-both-worlds-remote-ceo-says-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Keith%20Pitt%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20tech%20firm%20Buildkite%2C%20prefers%20remote%20work%20to%20hybrid%20setups%2C%20saying%20that's%20a%20%26quot%3Bscheduling%20and%20policy%20nightmare.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhybrid-work-worst-of-both-worlds-remote-ceo-says-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20games%3A%20How%20to%20find%20and%20play%20iconic%20games%20like%20Snake%20and%20Pac%20Man%20hidden%20in%20your%20browser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Pac%20Man%20Google%20Doodle%20game%20features%20the%20Google%20logo%20as%20a%20maze%2C%20with%20the%20iconic%20yellow%20circular%20character%20%26quot%3Beating%26quot%3B%20dots%20and%20dodging%20colorful%20ghosts.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644eb317415a05fdd088b00%3Ffo