l%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fact%20Check%3A%20Can%20Covaxin%20Lead%20To%20Death%20After%202%20Years%20Of%20Vaccination%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuick%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20social%20media%20user%2C%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%20can%20cause%20death%20after%20two%20years%20of%20vaccination.%20The%20user%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20Covaxin%20has%20caused%20the%20deaths%20of%20crores%20of%20people.%20We%20did%20the%20fact%20check%20and%20it%20came%20out%20to%20be%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20X%20user%20has%20shared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FBu42j%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20which%20claims%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20caused%20the%20death%20of%20crores%20of%20people%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fkchfi1_covaxin-factcheck_625x300_18_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFact%20Check%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20true%20that%20Covaxin%20can%20cause%20death%20even%20after%20two%20years%20of%20vaccination%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%20cannot%20cause%20death%20two%20years%20after%20vaccination.%20As%20of%20the%20latest%20available%20information%2C%20there%20is%20no%20conclusive%20evidence%20linking%20Covaxin%2C%20developed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bharatbiotech.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBharat%20Biotech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20attacks%20or%20death%20occurring%20two%20years%20post-vaccination.%20Vaccines%2C%20including%20Covaxin%2C%20undergo%20rigorous%20testing%20for%20safety%20and%20efficacy%20before%20approval%20and%20continued%20monitoring%20even%20after%20approval.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20adverse%20events%20following%20vaccination%20can%20occur.%20But%2C%20these%20are%20generally%20observed%20within%20a%20short%20period%20after%20vaccination%2C%20and%20long-term%20severe%20side%20effects%20are%20extremely%20rare.%20Covaxin%20was%20approved%20for%20emergency%20use%20by%20the%20WHO%2C%20after%20a%20complete%20risk-benefit%20analysis.%20Moreover%2C%20vaccines%20are%20the%20most%20important%20tool%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20any%20disease.%20We%20must%20also%20remember%20we%20were%20combating%20a%20pandemic%20at%20that%20time.%20As%20we%20have%20stated%20it%20earlier%2C%20vaccines%20have%20saved%20lives%20and%20have%20helped%20in%20controlling%20the%20spread%20of%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20consider%20that%20heart%20attacks%20and%20other%20cardiovascular%20events%20can%20occur%20due%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20underlying%20health%20conditions%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20genetic%20predispositions.%20These%20events%20happening%20two%20years%20post-vaccination%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20directly%20related%20to%20the%20vaccine%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWere%20there%20clinical%20trials%20of%20the%20Covaxin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%20underwent%20extensive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bharatbiotech.com%2Fimages%2Fpress%2Fcovaxin-clinical-trials-cross-23000-subjects.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclinical%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20June%202020%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20in%20India%20gave%20permission%20to%20start%20Phase%20I%20and%20II%20human%20trials%20for%20Covaxin%20after%20preclinical%20studies%20showed%20it%20was%20safe%20and%20produced%20a%20strong%20immune%20response%20in%20animals.%20Bharat%20Biotech%20conducted%20Phase%20I%20and%20Phase%20II%20trials%20involving%20approximately%201%2C000%20participants.%20These%20trials%20demonstrated%20promising%20safety%20and%20immunogenicity%20results%20and%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.12.21.20248643v1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.12.11.20210419v1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.09.09.285445v2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeer-reviewed%3C%2Fa%3E%20scientific%20journals.%20Following%20these%20initial%20phases%2C%20the%20Phase%20III%20clinical%20trials%20for%20Covaxin%20began%20in%20mid-November%2C%20targeting%20the%20recruitment%20of%2026%2C000%20volunteers%20across%20multiple%20sites%20in%20India.%20This%20was%20the%20largest%20Phase%20III%20efficacy%20trial%20ever%20conducted%20for%20any%20vaccine%20in%20India%2C%20marking%20India's%20first%20and%20only%20Phase%20III%20efficacy%20study%20for%20a%20COVID-19%20vaccine.%20The%20trials%20ensure%20the%20vaccine's%20safety%20and%20efficacy%20before%20approval%20and%20widespread%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20regulatory%20approvals%20has%20Covaxin%20received%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovaxin%20has%20received%20several%20significant%20regulatory%20approvals%20to%20ensure%20safety%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Drugs%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%20(DCGI)%20granted%20conditional%20market%20authorization%20for%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%20in%20January%202022.%20This%20approval%20followed%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Subject%20Expert%20Committee%20(SEC)%20of%20the%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organization%20(CDSCO)%20to%20upgrade%20the%20vaccine's%20status%20from%20restricted%20emergency%20use%2C%20which%20had%20been%20granted%20in%20January%202021.%20The%20CDSCO%20also%20approved%20its%20sale%20or%20distribution%20for%20restricted%20use%20in%20emergencies%20of%20public%20concern.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Covaxin%20received%20emergency%20use%20approval%20from%20the%20WHO%20in%20November%202021.%20However%2C%20in%20April%202022%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F02-04-2022-suspension-of-supply-of-covid-19-vaccine-covaxin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%20suspended%20the%20vaccine's%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20UN%20procurement%20agencies%20due%20to%20deficiencies%20in%20implementing%20good%20manufacturing%20practices%20(GMP).%20Bharat%20Biotech%20responded%20by%20suspending%20the%20production%20of%20Covaxin%20for%20export%20to%20address%20these%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnited%20States%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20December%202020%2C%20Bharat%20Biotech%20partnered%20with%20US-based%20biopharmaceutical%20company%20Ocugen%20to%20collaborate%20on%20the%20clinical%20development%2C%20registration%2C%20and%20commercialization%20of%20Covaxin%20for%20the%20US%20market.%20In%20February%202022%2C%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20lifted%20a%20clinical%20hold%20on%20Covaxin%2C%20allowing%20Phase%20II%2FIII%20clinical%20trials%20to%20proceed%20in%20support%20of%20a%20biologics%20licence%20application%20(BLA)%20submission.%20However%2C%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20FDA%20declined%20to%20issue%20an%20emergency%20use%20authorization%20(EUA)%20for%20Covaxin%20for%20paediatric%20patients%20aged%202%20to%2018%20years.%20Ocugen%20holds%20commercialization%20rights%20for%20Covaxin%20in%20North%20America%20and%20expanded%20these%20rights%20to%20include%20Mexico%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Countries%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Covaxin%20has%20received%20emergency%20use%20authorization%20for%20adults%20in%20Mexico%20and%20is%20approved%20for%20emergency%20use%20in%2020%20other%20countries.%20Covaxin%20is%20licensed%20for%20use%20in%2023%20countries%20worldwide%2C%20although%20its%20distribution%20is%20predominantly%20within%20India%2C%20where%20over%2077%20million%20doses%20have%20been%20administered%20as%20of%20June%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20the%20WHO%20suspend%20Covaxin's%20supply%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20stopped%20Covaxin%20supply%20for%20UN%20programs.%20This%20was%20because%20Bharat%20Biotech's%20main%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Hyderabad%20didn't%20fully%20follow%20good%20manufacturing%20practices%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Fquestions-and-answers%2Fitem%2Fmedicines-good-manufacturing-processes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGMP%3C%2Fa%3E).%20This%20happened%20because%20the%20facility%20had%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20making%20Covaxin%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20emergency.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20certain%20equipment%20needed%20for%20strict%20quality%20control%20wasn't%20available%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20Bharat%20Biotech%20emphasised%20that%20Covaxin's%20quality%20was%20never%20compromised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20WHO%20has%20also%20mentioned%20that%20this%20does%20not%20raise%20concern%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F02-04-2022-suspension-of-supply-of-covid-19-vaccine-covaxin%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520risk%2520assessment%2520to%2520date%2520does%2520not%2520indicate%2520changes%2520in%2520the%2520risk%25E2%2580%2593benefit%2520ratio.%2520The%2520data%252C%2520available%2520to%2520WHO%252C%2520indicate%2520the%2520vaccine%2520is%2520effective%2520and%2520no%2520safety%2520concerns%2520exist.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafety%20and%20efficacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Covaxin.%20It%20remains%20safe%20and%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20Covaxin%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovaxin%20is%20an%20inactivated%20vaccine%20developed%20from%20the%20SARS-CoV-2%20virus%2C%20meaning%20it%20uses%20a%20virus%20that%20has%20been%20killed%20and%20cannot%20cause%20COVID-19.%20When%20you%20receive%20the%20Covaxin%20shot%2C%20your%20immune%20system%20recognizes%20the%20inactivated%20virus%20and%20produces%20antibodies%20against%20it.%20These%20antibodies%20help%20your%20body%20fight%20off%20the%20virus%20if%20you%20are%20exposed%20to%20it%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20vaccine%20also%20includes%20substances%20called%20adjuvants%2C%20which%20enhance%20the%20immune%20response%20and%20help%20provide%20longer-lasting%20immunity.%20Covaxin%20is%20easy%20to%20store%2C%20as%20it%20only%20needs%20refrigeration%20between%202%E2%84%83%20to%208%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20effective%20is%20Covaxin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovaxin%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20be%2077.8%25%20effective%20against%20symptomatic%20COVID-19%20according%20to%20the%20final%20analysis%20of%20its%20Phase%20III%20trials.%20A%20booster%20dose%20six%20months%20after%20the%20second%20dose%20resulted%20in%20over%2075%25%20of%20participants%20having%20detectable%20neutralising%20antibodies%2C%20with%20even%20higher%20antibody%20levels%20than%20after%20the%20initial%20two%20doses.%20The%20booster%20also%20showed%20strong%20responses%20against%20the%20Omicron%20and%20Delta%20variants.%20Side%20effects%20are%20generally%20mild%2C%20including%20pain%20at%20the%20injection%20site%20and%20flu-like%20symptoms.%20Covaxin%20has%20also%20demonstrated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F38736802%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20efficacy%20in%20children%20compared%20to%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20side%20effects%20of%20Covaxin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovaxin%20may%20cause%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.cdc.gov%2F%23%2Fdetails%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fvaccines%2Fexpect%2Fafter.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emild%20side%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20pain%2C%20swelling%2C%20redness%2C%20or%20itching%20at%20the%20injection%20site%2C%20as%20well%20as%20body%20ache%2C%20weakness%2C%20stiffness%2C%20nausea%2C%20vomiting%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth%2Fgeneral-health%2Ffever%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efever%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20malaise%2C%20and%20headache.%20These%20effects%20are%20typically%20temporary%20and%20resolve%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20severe%20side%20effects%20or%20consequences%20of%20Covaxin%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35967168%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erare%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20can%20include%20allergic%20reactions%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fcovid-19%2Fclinical-considerations%2Fmanaging-anaphylaxis.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanaphylaxis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20crucial%20to%20seek%20immediate%20medical%20attention%20if%20you%20experience%20symptoms%20like%20difficulty%20in%20breathing%2C%20swelling%20of%20the%20face%20or%20throat%2C%20rapid%20heartbeat%2C%20or%20severe%20dizziness%20after%20vaccination.%20Additionally%2C%20while%20extremely%20rare%2C%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20blood%20clotting%20disorders%20associated%20with%20Covaxin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20it%20take%20for%20a%20side%20effect%20to%20occur%20after%20vaccination%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20vaccination%2C%20most%20people%20experience%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamadermatology%2Ffullarticle%2F2779643%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esore%20arm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20more%20widespread%20effects%20like%20fever%20and%20chills%20usually%20appearing%20within%208%20to%2012%20hours.%20These%20side%20effects%20usually%20resolve%20within%2048%20hours.%20Since%20the%20vaccine%20cannot%20cause%20a%20COVID-19%20infection%2C%20experiencing%20symptoms%20indicates%20a%20healthy%20immune%20response.%20While%20rare%2C%20allergic%20reactions%20can%20occur%20within%20the%20first%2015%20to%2030%20minutes%20after%20the%20jab.%20More%20common%20side%20effects%20include%20arm%20soreness%2C%20redness%2C%20and%20swelling%20at%20the%20injection%20site%2C%20with%20body-wide%20effects%20lasting%2012%20hours%20or%20more.%20Experts%20advise%20that%20these%20side%20effects%20generally%20cease%20within%2024%20to%2048%20hours%20after%20vaccination%2C%20although%20slight%20fatigue%20or%20arm%20soreness%20may%20persist.%20Comparing%2048%20hours%20of%20side%20effects%20to%20the%20risk%20of%20hospitalisation%20and%20death%20from%20COVID-19%2C%20experts%20emphasise%20the%20benefits%20of%20vaccination%20outweigh%20potential%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20reaction%20of%20the%20medical%20community%20regarding%20Covaxin's%20approval%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F373%2Fbmj.n997.long%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency%20approval%20of%20Covaxin%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20completing%20Phase%20III%20trials%20faced%20criticism%20from%20the%20Indian%20scientific%20community.%20Despite%20nearly%2014%20million%20COVID-19%20cases%2C%20approval%20came%20as%20cases%20were%20dropping.%20The%20CDSCO's%20vague%20term%20%E2%80%9Crestricted%20use%20in%20an%20emergency%20situation%E2%80%9D%20left%20many%20puzzled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroups%20like%20the%20All%20India%20People's%20Science%20Network%20called%20the%20approval%20%E2%80%9Chasty%2C%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20All%20India%20Drug%20Action%20Network%20demanded%20transparency.%20Concerns%20grew%20after%20a%20Phase%20III%20trial%20participant%20died%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20improper%20screening%20at%20the%20trial%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%2045%20doctors%2C%20including%20former%20AIIMS%20directors%2C%20defended%20Covaxin%2C%20calling%20it%20India's%20%E2%80%9Cgift%20to%20humanity%E2%80%9D%20and%20labelling%20the%20criticism%20as%20%E2%80%9Cirresponsible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20should%20you%20do%20in%20case%20you%20have%20concerns%20regarding%20vaccines%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20specific%20concerns%20about%20health%20conditions%20post-vaccination%2C%20it's%20advisable%20to%20consult%20with%20a%20healthcare%20professional.%20They%20can%20provide%20personalised%20medical%20advice%20and%20conduct%20any%20necessary%20evaluations.%20They%20can%20also%20help%20differentiate%20between%20vaccine-related%20issues%20and%20other%20potential%20causes%20of%20health%20problems.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20make%20it%20clear%2C%20one%20should%20not%20trust%20random%20and%20unreliable%20social%20media%20posts%20for%20making%20their%20healthcare%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20the%20authorities%20watching%20for%20heart%20problems%20after%20COVID-19%20vaccines%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20CDC%20and%20other%20notable%20organisations%20have%20been%20actively%20monitoring%20COVID-19%20vaccine-induced%20myocarditis.%20They%20provide%20transparent%2C%20evidence-based%20information%20on%20vaccine%20safety%20and%20participate%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fteams%2Fregulation-prequalification%2Fregulation-and-safety%2Fpharmacovigilance%2Fnetworks%2Fvaccine-safety-net%2Fvsn-members%2Fcenters-for-disease-control-and-prevention%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO-led%20Vaccine%20Safety%20Net%20project%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20CDC%20has%20launched%20investigations%20into%20myocarditis%20and%20pericarditis%20cases.%20Especially%20following%20mRNA%20vaccinations%20(Covaxin%20is%20an%20inactivated%20virus%20vaccine)%2C%20with%20active%20surveillance%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fcovid-19%2Fclinical-considerations%2Fmyocarditis.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20adolescents%20and%20young%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20the%20CDC%20fight%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20misinformation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20actively%20combats%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fcovid-19%2Fhealth-departments%2Faddressing-vaccine-misinformation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20misinformation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20address%20false%20information%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20CDC%20uses%20a%20multimodal%20approach.%20It%20provides%20credible%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fvaccines%2Ffacts.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevidence-based%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fvaccines%2Fsafety%2Fadverse-events.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaccine%20safety%20and%20adverse%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20its%20website%20and%20collaborates%20with%20health%20organizations.%20The%20CDC%20also%20uses%20social%20media%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20public%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Fquestions-and-answers%2Fitem%2Fcoronavirus-disease-(covid-19)-vaccines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edispel%20myths%20about%20COVID-19%20vaccines%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20would%20like%20to%20conclude%20with%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cstrong%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20COVID%20vaccines%20far%20outweigh%20the%20associated%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20debunked%20several%20claims%20regarding%20the%20COVID%20vaccines.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Ffact-check-was-covid-handling-by-the-government-of-india-a-huge-scam%2F62061%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWas%20COVID%20handling%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20a%20huge%20scam%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Ffact-check-has-japans-government-banned-the-covid-19-vaccine%2F62069%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHas%20Japan's%20government%20banned%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccine%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Ffact-check-has-the-german-government-admitted-there-was-no-pandemic%2F62116%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20German%20government%20admitted%20there%20was%20no%20Pandemic%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Ffact-check-has-japan-declared-an-emergency-over-the-explosion-of-mrna-cancers%2F62972%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHas%20Japan%20declared%20an%20emergency%20over%20the%20%E2%80%98explosion%20of%20mRNA%20cancers'%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Ffact-check-are-indians-with-covishield-susceptible-to-developing-tts%2F63120%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAre%20Covishield-vaccinated%20Indians%20susceptible%20to%20developing%20TTS%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thip.media%2Fhealth-news-fact-check%2Fcan-covaxin-cause-death-after-two-years-of-vaccination%2F65554%2F%5C%22%3ETHIP%20Media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-td-block-uid%3D%5C%22tdi_153%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-page-id%3D%5C%2251305%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20data-pin-description%3D%5C%22A%20post%20on%20X%20claims%20Covaxin%20COVID%20vaccine%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20crores%20of%20people.%20Our%20fact%20check%20termed%20it%20as%20false.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.thip.media%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F17115647%2Fcaucasian-man-with-vaccination-for-covid-19-2019-2023-11-27-04-53-05-utc-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv