nment%20to%20take%20action%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Gowda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%2C%20the%20former%20PM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20people%20connected%20to%20these%20sexual%20abuse%20cases.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20mention%20anyone's%20names.%20Kumaraswamy%20has%20stated%20that%20those%20involved%20in%20this%20matter%20should%20face%20action%2C%20and%20the%20affected%20women%20should%20get%20justice%20and%20compensation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20objection%20from%20us%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20Prajwal.%20But%20people%20have%20come%20to%20know%20the%20facts%20about%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20Revanna%2C%20how%20the%20case%20has%20been%20created.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20he%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%2C%20and%20in%20another%20case%2C%20the%20judgment%20is%20expected%20day%20after%20tomorrow...%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20concurring%20with%20Kumaraswamy's%20statement%20that%20if%20found%20guilty%2C%20no%20one%20should%20be%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20(33)%20is%20facing%20charges%20of%20multiple%20instances%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20women.%20The%20scandal%20has%20sparked%20a%20political%20storm%20with%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20BJP-JD(S)%20engaged%20in%20a%20slugfest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20reportedly%20left%20for%20Germany%20on%20April%2027%20and%20is%20still%20at%20large.%20An%20Interpol%20Blue%20Corner%20Notice%20has%20been%20issued%20against%20him%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20bring%20him%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20alliance's%20joint%20candidate%20from%20the%20Hassan%20Lok%20Sabha%20segment%2C%20which%20went%20to%20polls%20on%20April%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Gowda's%2066-year-old%20son%2C%20Revanna%2C%20a%20former%20Minister%2C%20has%20been%20granted%20interim%20anticipatory%20bail%20from%20a%20court%20here%20in%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20in%20which%20his%20son%20Prajwal%20is%20also%20an%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20defame%20and%20politically%20scuttle%20his%20family%2C%20Gowda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true...%20considering%20all%20that%20has%20happened%2C%20several%20people%20are%20involved.%20I%20won't%20mention%20names.%20Kumaraswamy%20will%20address%20what%20action%20needs%20to%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20query%20on%20BJP%20leader%20and%20advocate%20G%20Devaraje%20Gowda's%20allegations%20that%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20is%20behind%20the%20circulation%20of%20a%20pen%20drive%20containing%20explicit%20videos%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20Gowda%20said%20Kumaraswamy%20will%20respond%20to%20all%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20media%20what%20Devaraje%20Gowda%20has%20said.%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20as%20the%20party's%20state%20President%2C%20has%20been%20actively%20responding%20to%20all%20this.%20He%20will%20speak.%20I%20won't%20at%20this%20point.%20I%20had%20campaigned%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20On%20June%204%2C%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%20are%20announced%2C%20I%20will%20meet%20with%20you%20(media)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGowda%20also%20appealed%20to%20media%20persons%20campaigning%20near%20his%20house%20to%20end%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20appeal%20to%20your%20owners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716017580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Flklql2bg_prajwal-revanna_625x300_18_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeve-gowda-breaks-silence-on-grandson-prajwal-revannas-sexual-abuse-case-no-objection-to-action-if-guilty-