n%20the%20IPL%202024%20match.%20RCB%20have%20an%20unblemished%20record%20in%20games%20played%20on%20May%2018%2C%20but%20rain%20could%20disrupt%20their%20hopes.%20To%20secure%20the%20final%20playoff%20berth%2C%20they%20need%20a%20significant%20win%20over%20CSK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fvirat-kohlis-cosmic-connection-with-18-ex-india-player-highlights-rcbs-perfect-record-on-may-18-ahead-of-ipl-clash-with-csk%2Farticleshow%2F110226148.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bullied%2C%20Shunned%20At%20School%2C%20Himachal%20Trans%20Woman%20Is%20Now%20An%20'Election%20Icon'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAbuse%20by%20students%20and%20reluctance%20on%20the%20part%20of%20teachers%20to%20take%20action%20compelled%20her%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20after%20class%20IX%2C%20says%20Maya%20Thakur%2C%20the%20transgender%20icon%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20State%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20Kothi%20village%20in%20Kunihar%20area%20of%20the%20Solan%20district%20under%20Shimla%20parliamentary%20constituency%2C%20Ms%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20had%20become%20so%20grim%20that%20villagers%20started%20pressuring%20her%20family%20to%20%26quot%3Bthrow%20her%20out%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20transgender%20among%2035%20belonging%20to%20the%20third%20gender%20in%20the%20state%2C%20who%20gathered%20the%20courage%20to%20speak%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20used%20to%20tell%20my%20family%20members%20about%20the%20ill-treatment%20and%20discrimination%20in%20the%20school%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20use%20the%20toilet%2C%20they%20thought%20I%20was%20making%20excuses%20to%20skip%20the%20school.%20Given%20a%20chance%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20resume%20my%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20lamenting%20that%20she%20faced%20discrimination%20at%20%26quot%3Bevery%20step%20in%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEducation%2C%20jobs%20and%20ending%20discrimination%20against%20transgenders%20are%20our%20main%20issues.%20There%20are%20transgenders%20who%20wish%20to%20study%2C%20become%20teachers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20join%20the%20police%20and%20excel%20in%20other%20spheres%20of%20life%20but%20when%20we%20apply%20for%20jobs%2C%20the%20response%20is%20'will%20tell%20you%20if%20there%20is%20any%20scheme%20for%20you'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20born%20as%20a%20male%20but%20identified%20myself%20as%20a%20woman.%20My%20identity%20is%20that%20of%20a%20transgender%20woman%2C%20we%20are%20unisex%20and%20not%20eunuchs%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20are%20not%20accepted%20in%20society%20as%20people%20consider%20them%20eunuchs%20and%20maintain%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20still%20better%20in%20south%20India%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20north%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20spread%20awareness%20for%20social%20acceptability%20for%20transgenders%2C%20who%20have%20the%20right%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20she%20said.%20She%20also%20blamed%20the%20police%20for%20not%20registering%20their%20complaints%20against%20high%20handedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%2C%20who%20earlier%20worked%20at%20an%20NGO%20in%20Delhi%2C%20advocates%20for%20lessons%20on%20transgenders%20in%20educational%20curriculum%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20countries%20like%20Canada%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20the%20right%20to%20an%20educational%20environment%20free%20from%20discrimination%20and%20harassment%20and%20use%20of%20bathrooms%20that%20correspond%20with%20their%20gender%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20eunuch%20culture%20of%20extorting%20money%20by%20threatening%20or%20cursing%20should%20be%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Besides%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20eunuchs%20taking%20away%20transgenders%20or%20harassing%20them%2C%20and%20people%20indulging%20in%20such%20acts%20should%20attract%20legal%20action%2C%20she%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716014400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5u2u74fc_transgender-woman-maya-thakur-himachal-ec-icon-pti_625x300_18_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbullied-and-shunned-at-school-himachal-transgender-woman-is-now-an-election-icon-5689753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abuse%20by%20students%20and%20reluctance%20on%20the%20part%20of%20teachers%20to%20take%20action%20compelled%20her%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20after%20class%20IX%2C%20says%20Maya%20Thakur%2C%20the%20transgender%20icon%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20State%20Election%20Commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbullied-and-shunned-at-school-himachal-transgender-woman-is-now-an-election-icon-5689753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbullied-and-shunned-at-school-himachal-transgender-woman-is-now-an-election-icon-5689753%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbullied-and-shunned-at-school-himachal-transgender-woman-is-now-an-election-icon-5689753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DYK%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%20had%20a%20pic%20of%20Sonali%20Bendre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716014071000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110226027%2Cimgsize-46750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdi