%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110223739.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit's%20Smashing%20Reply%20When%20Asked%20By%20MI%20Coach%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20Next%3F%26quot%3B%20On%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20the%20IPL%202024%20season%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20points%20table%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20head%20coach%20Mark%20Boucher%20looked%20back%20and%20spoke%20his%20heart%20on%20a%20number%20of%20challenges%20the%20team%20faced%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20After%20losing%20to%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%2C%20Mumbai's%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20season%20came%20to%20an%20abrupt%20end%2C%20finishing%20last%20in%20the%20IPL%20standings.%20As%20MI's%20disastrous%20season%20ended%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20Boucher%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20future%20of%20former%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20with%20the%20team%20and%20the%20head%20coach%20said%20that%20the%20opener%20is%20a%20master%20of%20his%20own%20destiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20MI's%20last%20match%20of%20the%20season%2C%20opener%20Rohit%20showed%20the%20erratic%20nature%20of%20T20I%20by%20going%20through%20a%20slump%20after%20a%20bright%20start%20to%20the%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20he%20is%20a%20master%20of%20his%20own%20destiny.%20It's%20a%20big%20auction%20next%20season%20who%20knows%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20Boucher%20said%20in%20a%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20former%20MI%20skipper's%20performance%2C%20Boucher%20said%20it%20was%20a%20season%20of%20two%20halves%20for%20the%20opener%20as%20he%20had%20a%20strong%20start%20to%20the%20season%20and%20hammered%20the%20ball%20well%20into%20the%20netting.%20The%20head%20coach%20also%20said%20that%20Rohit%20was%20headed%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20so%20that%20we%20could%20run%20some%20excellent%20races.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20discussion%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma%20last%20night.%20We%20reviewed%20the%20season%20this%20year.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20what's%20next%3F%20and%20Rohit%20said%20'the%20World%20Cup'%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20on%20Friday%2C%20Rohit%20broke%20a%20run%20of%20poor%20scores%20when%20he%20struck%20an%20incredible%2068%20off%2038%20deliveries%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20match%20against%20LSG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20a%20season%20of%20two%20halves%20for%20him.%20He%20started%20the%20season%20well%20and%20hit%20the%20ball%20sweetly%20in%20the%20nets.%20He%20got%20a%20superb%20100%20against%20CSK%20as%20well.%20So%20we%20honestly%20thought%20he%20was%20on%20a%20great%20path%20for%20us%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20get%20some%20good%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Boucher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20season%20beset%20by%20controversy%20for%20the%20MI%2C%20Rohit's%20batting%20performance%20was%20as%20inconsistent.%20Rohit's%20fortunes%20collapsed%20after%20he%20made%20a%20promising%20start%20to%20the%20season%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20century%20against%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20but%20in%20his%20next%20six%20appearances%2C%20the%20opener%20was%20dismissed%20on%20four%20single-digit%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20it's%20just%20the%20nature%20of%20T20%20as%20well.%20He%20went%20out%20there%20trying%20to%20be%20aggressive%2C%20the%20new%20way%20of%20playing%20as%20an%20opening%20batter.%20He%20got%20a%20few%20low%20scores%2C%20which%20unfortunately%20didn't%20help%20us%20in%20that%20particular%20situation%20either.%20But%20tonight%2C%20he%20finished%20off%20with%20a%20fantastic%20knock%20as%20well.%20So%20yeah%2C%20it%20is%20a%20season%20of%20two%20halves%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20fans%20had%20mixed%20emotions%20on%20a%20bittersweet%20evening%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%20While%20they%20were%20thrilled%20with%20Rohit's%20explosive%20fifty%20but%20also%20witnessed%20their%20team%20suffer%20their%20tenth%20loss%20of%20the%20year%20and%20drop%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20points%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Naman%20Dhir's%20fiery%20knocks%20went%20in%20vain%20as%20MI%20conceded%20an%2018-run%20loss%20against%20LSG%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20match%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20the%20toss%20MI%20sent%20LSG%20to%20bat%20first%20but%20that%20did%20not%20go%20in%20their%20favour%20as%20KL%20Rahul%20(55%20runs%20from%2041%20balls%2C%203%20fours%20and%203%20sixes)%20and%20Nicholas%20Pooran%20(75%20runs%20from%2029%20balls%2C%205%20fours%20and%208%20sixes)%20played%20a%20fiery%20knock%20in%20the%20first%20inning.%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20(28%20runs%20from%2022%20balls%2C%205%20fours)%20and%20Ayush%20Badoni%20(22*%20runs%20from%2010%20balls%2C%201%20four%20and%202%20sixes)%20were%20the%20other%20standout%20batters%20for%20LSG%20as%20they%20propelled%20the%20visitors%20to%20214%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20the%20hosts%20had%20a%20stupendous%20start%20while%20chasing%20a%20215-run%20target%20but%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fourth%20over%2C%20rain%20played%20a%20spoilsport%20for%20which%20the%20game%20was%20halted%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20However%2C%20that%20did%20not%20break%20the%20MI%20openers'%20momentum%20as%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(68%20runs%20from%2038%20balls%2C%2010%20fours%20and%203%20sixes)%20and%20Dewald%20Brevis%20(23%20runs%20from%2020%20balls%2C%201%20four%20and%202%20sixes)%20played%20a%20partnership%20of%2088%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaman%20Dhir's%20(62*%20runs%20from%2028%20balls%2C%204%20fours%20a