re%20a%20plastic-neutral%20brand%2C%20wherein%20all%20the%20plastic%20that%20they%20are%20using%20is%20recycled.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20process%20about%2030%20percent%20directly%2C%20while%20we%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20processes%20the%20remaining.%20It%20is%20converted%20into%20biofuel%20and%20supplied%20to%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20Elements%20is%20a%20certified%20%E2%80%98Clean%20Label%E2%80%99%20brand%20by%20the%20Clean%20Label%20Project%2C%20US%2C%20and%20100%20percent%20whole%20grain%20brand%20by%20the%20Whole%20Grains%20Council%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20presence%20built%20around%20300%20towns%20in%20India%20with%20over%20300%20employees%2C%20supplying%20to%20over%20five%20lakh%20households%20every%20month%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20working%20towards%20their%20mission%20of%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indians.%20They%20are%20clear%20on%20their%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20clean%20food%20%E2%80%94%20the%20reason%20they%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20like%20protein%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20their%20message%20to%20budding%20entrepreneurs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20overthink%2C%20just%20start%20up.%20There%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfect%20time.%20Dive%20in%20with%20a%20childlike%20mindset%2C%20and%20just%20like%20children%20do%20when%20they%20fall%20down%2C%20stand%20up%20and%20try%20again.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fall%20down%20and%20fail.%20Shun%20the%20need%20for%20validation%20and%20fear%20of%20judgement%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3