s-of-sex-workers-kamathipura-international-university%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Expensive%20Mango%2C%20Lotus%20With%201000%20Petals%20%26amp%3B%20More%3A%20Engineer%20Grows%20400%20Plants%20at%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20Subrat%20Nath%2C%20going%20on%20a%20shopping%20spree%20equals%20visiting%20plant%20nurseries.%20He%20considers%20this%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20upbeat%20activities%20for%20him.%20On%20one%20such%20trip%2C%20the%20florist%20there%20introduced%20him%20to%20a%20sapling%20that%20was%20said%20to%20produce%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347996%2Frare-mangoes-available-in-india-alphonso-sindhri-mango-expensive-mangoes-summer-season%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMiyazaki%2520Mango%26amp%3Btext%3DIn%2520India%252C%2520only%2520a%2520few%2Cconditions%2520to%2520ensure%2520optimal%2520quality.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecostliest%20mangoes%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20Miyazaki!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rare%20mango%20is%20native%20to%20Miyazaki%20city%20in%20Japan.%20It%20has%20a%20violet-red%20colour%20and%20is%20comparatively%20sweeter%2C%20juicier%2C%20and%20larger%20than%20other%20mango%20varieties%2C%20including%20the%20famous%20Alphonso%20mangoes.%20I%20was%20so%20fascinated%20by%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fruit%20has%20an%20unusual%20appearance%20like%20an%20egg%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Eggs%20of%20Sun.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20these%20mangoes%20are%20sold%20at%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20international%20market.%20Subrat%20cites%20their%20medicinal%20properties%20for%20their%20exorbitant%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%2