e%20market%20early%20on%2C%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20greater%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20enthusiastic%20about%20learning%20farming%20from%20the%20farmers%20in%20Israel%20and%20decided%20to%20try%20it%20out%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20cut%20short%20an%20internship%20I%20was%20doing%20at%20the%20time%20and%20go%20to%20Israel.%20I%20found%20a%20farmer%20who%20was%20gracious%20enough%20to%20help%20me%20learn%20the%20entire%20process.%20I%20stayed%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20taught%20me%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20healthy%20avocadoes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20his%20routine%20in%20Israel%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daily%20routine%20there%20started%20with%20waking%20up%20at%205%20am.%20We%20would%20work%20in%20the%20fields%20only%20during%20the%20morning%20hours%20until%2010.%20Then%2C%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20he%20would%20introduce%20me%20to%20various%20industry%20experts%2C%20such%20as%20the%20greenhouse%20managers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340703%2Fkota-student-aryan-singh-invented-ai-powered-agrobot-runs-on-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirrigation%20specialists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20exporters%2C%20and%20marketers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20training%20period%2C%20he%20invited%20them%20to%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20my%20farmer%20friends%20over%20in%202018.%20My%20mentor%20and%20the%20nursery%20owner%20conducted%20soil%20tests%20and%20assessed%20the%20climate%20conditions%20in%20Bhopal.%20They%20also%20visited%20other%20farms%20growing%20citrus%20and%20mango.%20After%20evaluating%20the%20area%2C%20they%20suggested%20that%20a%20garden%20could%20thrive%20in%20Bhopal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20identified%20specific%20avocado%20varieties%20that%20would%20be%20suitable%20for%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20while%20India%20lacks%20high-quality%20avocados%20and%20specific%20varieties%2C%20Israel%20has%20excellent%20rootstocks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20import%20these%20rootstocks%20from%20Israel%20and%20began%20planning%20his%20first%20consignment%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20import%20process%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20lengthy%2C%20complicated%2C%20and%20full%20of%20regulations%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20adhere%20to.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20struggled%20with%20the%20import%20procedure%2C%20causing%20my%20consignment%20to%20be%20delayed%20until%202020%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C