have%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%20This%20is%20a%20small%20step%20towards%20a%20big%20issue%20but%20it%20can%20be%20replicated%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20to%20reduce%20the%20root%20cause%20and%20frequency%20of%20forest%20fires%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sharvari%20Poharkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Futtarakhand-wildfire-forest-fires-death-toll-rain-forecast-pushkar-singh-dhami-revenue-loss-2535698-2024-05-06%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%20dead%20in%20Uttarakhand%20wildfires%2C%20over%201%2C000%20hectares%20of%20forest%20destroyed%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20Ankit%20Sharma%20for%20India%20Today%2C%20published%20on%206%20May%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Funder-age-chir-pine-trees-being-illegally-extracted-for-resin-in-ukhand%2Farticleshow%2F103336870.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnder-age%20chir%20pine%20trees%20being%20illegally%20extracted%20for%20resin%20in%20U%E2%80%99khand%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20Shivani%20Azad%20for%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20published%20on%204%20September%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715766211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-3-1-1715764011.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349983%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202021%2C%20Nupur%20and%20Sharvari%20Poharkar%20started%20%E2%80%98PIRUL%20Handicrafts%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20useful%2